Title: MyLNI
Description: MyLNI represents the first major expansion of the Washington State Labor & Industries eGovernment initiative. This project is a wrapper application for the many individual applications within the LNI ecosystem. I performed work implementing the UI for the Employer Dashboard, an aggregate visualization of primary LNI entities, including claims, insurance accounts, and general safety information.
Tech: Backbone, Marionette, Underscore, Jquery, ES5, Sass, Require, Node, Bower, Gulp, Grunt, .NET, VB
